        Hi! I'm a M.S. student in the{' '}
        <a href="https://larr.snu.ac.kr/">Lab for Autonomous Robotics Research</a>{' '} (LARR)
        at Seoul National University (SNU), advised by <a href="https://scholar.google.co.kr/citations?user=TLQUwIMAAAAJ&hl=en">Prof. H. Jin Kim</a>. 
        I've received my B.S. in Mechanical and Aerospace Engineering from SNU in Fall 2024.
